---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Kurulum" description="Docufy kurulum adımları ve PATH ayarı">
  <h2>Go ile kurulum</h2>
  <pre><code>go install github.com/mlihgenel/docufy/v2/cmd/docufy@latest</code></pre>

  <h2>PATH ayarı</h2>
  <p>
    `go env GOBIN` doluysa o dizini, boş ise `$(go env GOPATH)/bin` dizinini PATH'e eklemelisin.
  </p>
  <pre><code>echo 'export PATH="$PATH:$(go env GOPATH)/bin"' >> ~/.zshrc
source ~/.zshrc</code></pre>

  <h2>Kontrol</h2>
  <pre><code>docufy --version
docufy --help</code></pre>

  <h2>Kaynaktan derleme</h2>
  <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/mlihgenel/docufy.git
cd docufy
go build -o docufy ./cmd/docufy
./docufy --help</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
